## CI/CD Safety
- Never commit `public/build/` (gitignored)
- Never commit `.env` or secrets
- If deploy fails, check: SSH keys, GitHub Secrets, build process
- Staging: `ssh -p 2223 jogn3455@jogjatourdrive.com` (deploy target)
- App: `https://zonakasir.jogjatourdrive.com` (staging hostname)

## Commit + Build Rule
When instructed to `commit` and `build`:
- Stage ALL workspace changes (`git add -A`)
- Do NOT create partial commits (unless user explicitly requests)
- If there are unrelated/risky changes, pause and ask first
- Verify with `git status --porcelain` before committing
- After commit, push triggers auto-deploy via CI/CD
- **Do NOT build locally** тАФ CI handles `npm run build`

## Security Baseline
- Auth check server-side on every protected endpoint
- Validation lengkap (bukan type-only) тАФ `FormRequest` classes with complex rules
- RBAC permission check with `can()` helper (Filament) + `->can()` middleware (API)
- No hardcoded secrets or credentials (GitHub Secrets for CI/CD)
- API responses via `ApiResponseService` (consistent format)
- Rate limiting on critical endpoints (`throttle:5,1` on auth, `throttle:60,1` on tenant routes)
- Audit logging via `spatie/laravel-activitylog` on 14 models (Member, Supplier, Stock, PaymentMethod, CashDrawer, Voucher, etc.)

## Commit Conventions

Format: `type(scope): description`

| Type | When |
|------|------|
| `fix` | Bug fix |
| `feat` | New feature |
| `refactor` | Code restructure |
| `style` | UI/CSS only |
| `perf` | Performance |
| `ci` | CI/CD workflow changes |
| `docs` | Documentation |
| `chore` | Tooling, deps, config |

## Branch Naming

**Strategy:** Dual-branch: `main` (VPS/MySQL/production) and `vercel` (PostgreSQL/Vercel test). **Never merge `vercel` into `main`** тАФ branches are separate forever.

| Branch | DB | Hosting | Purpose | Auto-deploy |
|--------|----|---------|---------|-------------|
| `main` | MySQL 8.0 | VPS (Docker) | Production-ready staging | тЬЕ VPS via GHA |
| `vercel` | PostgreSQL 15 | Vercel (serverless) | Vercel deployment testing (тЪая╕П 250MB limit) | тЭМ Manual via CLI |
| `feat/*` | тАФ | тАФ | Feature branches (delete after merge) | тЭМ No |
| `fix/*` | тАФ | тАФ | Bug fix branches (delete after merge) | тЭМ No |
| `1.x` | MySQL | тАФ | Maintenance branch for v1.x | тЭМ No |

